schools.name: Youree Dr. Middle Advanced Placement Magnet School

data.description: Charming, well-maintained townhome with new countertops, flooring and carpet is 6 years old, and new windows. Inside was totally painted 2 years ago, and insulation blown in.  Water heater is one year old.  The fridge and washer and dryer to remain. Loction is superb being close to restaurants, shopping, doctors, and hospitals. Close to I-49 and Inner-loop 3132.  The furniture in the home is for sale. The HOA dues of $180 a month include the water, trash pick up, yard and common area maintenance, painting the exterior and includes the Community pool, and the community Tennis (pickle ball) courts.
